1)If cost price and selling price of an item input through the keyboard write a program to determine whether the seller has made profit or increased loss .Also determine much profit he made or loss he increased.
Ans :
cost_price = float(input("Enter Cost Price: "))
selling_price = float(input("Enter Selling Price: "))
if selling_price > cost_price:
    profit = selling_price - cost_price
    print("Seller made a Profit of =", profit)
elif cost_price > selling_price:
    loss = cost_price - selling_price
    print("Seller incurred a Loss of =", loss)
else:
    print("No Profit, No Loss")
